name: Canberra

venue.name: Canberra Grammar School - The Snow Centre
venue.accessibility: Venue is accessible from the main school carpark via footpaths. The Snow Centre has a lift which provides access to all levels of the building.
venue.under_18: At this Venue you must be accompanied by a Guardian at all times
venue.childcare: There will be no childcare arrangements at this event.
venue.public_transport: ACTION buses depart from the bus stop on Golden Grove, next to the Snow Centre.
venue.parking: Parking is available in the main school carparks off Monaro Crescent. Note, there will be a large number of sporting matches taking place on the school ovals on Saturday morning so it is advisable to arrive early to GovHack otherwise parking could be difficult.
venue.public_transport_last: Check the ACTION website for details.
